# Android / Kotlin Rules

- Use Jetpack Compose for the sample Settings screen.
- Platform-native controls (Material Switch, Material top app bar) are **hold** candidates.
- Brand tokens (colors, spacing scale, typography) are **propagate** candidates.
- Prefer design tokens over hardcoded `Color(0xFF...)` values. Hardcoded values are **flag** candidates.
- Minimum touch target: 48dp.
- System font is Roboto (hold). Brand font changes propagate.
